  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a study of recurrent crying spells in Spastic Cerebral Palsy patients and their
      treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is the first study of recurrent crying spells in Cerebral Palsy with Spastic
      quadriparesis depicting the diagnostic criteria and treatment.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
